{"tid":2380942,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB配音員東東爆離巢真相 唔想再講難聽惡心反胃Slogan","createTime":"2021-01-26T08:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T21:37:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":127,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c2cc054df85427a1dbec5dbf529d69ae5d46d249","tid":2380942,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"90年代《閃電傳真機》童星「東東」張裕東（現改名張預東）本月初裸辭效力了22年的TVB，昨日他在YouTube分享了自己離巢的原因，由童星轉做配音的他，認為一個表演要成立，要有表演者和觀眾，但他覺得舊公司跟觀眾對立，兼不聽觀眾意見，無論表演質素多高，工作人員如何付出心血，也是付諸流水，「只要觀眾見到你個Logo已經想嘔，係浪費咗好多表演者嘅心機。」<br />\n<br />\n東東自言TVB的觀眾，跟他的目標觀眾是兩極化，「我根本唔想為呢批人表演，我做咩要表演畀佢哋睇呢！咁辛苦，所以我咪走囉！如果你仍然鍾意睇TVB我尊重你，你覺得好睇咪繼續睇。」他坦言近幾年講了太多不想說出口的口號，舉例有「全港第一」、「領先全球」，而最難聽亦令他覺得惡心的一句是「帶領樂壇」，他嚴肅地說：「講起都反胃，好多年前做TVB好威風，個個都好想你帶入TVB影張相，又想攞門票睇《獎門人》同《勁歌》。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210126/OZOZAWH47JAUBCW4PCN5A5SMMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210126%2FOZOZAWH47JAUBCW4PCN5A5SMMI%2F&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=1035527b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210126%2FOZOZAWH47JAUBCW4PCN5A5SMMI%2F&h=353e43ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210126/OZOZAWH47JAUBCW4PCN5A5SMMI/</a>"},{"pid":"d1afba74eaad2d6ae353f6623e6653c5998590b8","tid":2380942,"uid":114097,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n諗緊成個配音組係咪得陳欣可以講完呢啲嘢又唔打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5eca232de9bb7a4dc1d452342545cdd6d4e63e","tid":2380942,"uid":70505,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"早排個廣告話年輕人觀眾領先全港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽到我o晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets